		SHIELD BASH
Bash your opponent with a shield.
This can causes more damage than but.
If you try to bash again too early then there will be a long time until you
are able to do another shield bash.
You obviously need a shield.
You can`t do it if you are recovering from a but.
You must be in a fight.
The damage done by your bash varies from bash to bash and according to certain
stats.
eg bash
